      "path": "audio/narrations/burning-ship/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "燃烧船只比曼德博多了一步绝对值，却换来全新的船形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "burning-ship",
      "section_id": "summary",
